<br>
<br>
The reason people will pay 15pp for a silk swatch is because they feel their time is more valuable than their money. If you have 300kpp in the bank and would like to become a GM tailor... Will you go spend hours farming silks or go to bazaar and pay someone else to do it?<br>
<br>
On the flip side, if you have 0kpp then spending a couple of hours to get 200 silks and selling them for 15pp is a GREAT use of your time.<br>
<br>
It doesn't mean that one way is better than the other, it's just that people have different priorities. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=raiyaeq>RaiyaEQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I Live Here</span><br>  Posts: 1085<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(8/8/03 8:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2122.topic&index=58>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> yes</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>If you have 300kpp in the bank and would like to become a GM tailor... Will you go spend hours farming silks or go to bazaar and pay someone else to do it?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
