<br>
Farming is horrible.  Many of us really do not enjoy it, me included.  Raiya has a high tolerance for it, and it works for her, but most of us would rather kill Talendor, sell a CoF, and buy 15 points of tailoring components with the proceeds than spend 30 hours killing rockhoppers.<br>
